          "name": "Permission to Create Before You're Ready",
          "version": "1.0.0",
          "description": "A motivational guide about overcoming perfectionism and productive procrastination to just start creating",
          "createdAt": "2026-03-03T21:00:00.000Z",
          "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T21:00:00.000Z"
